PrecisDefinition of Indians, Métis, Inuit and non-status Indians of Canada, and legal entities owned or controlled by any of them, as a category of persons in respect of which the Minister of Industry, Science and Technology may develop and implement programs and projects of special assistance to aid economic development.

precis:
Definition of Indians, Métis, Inuit and non-status Indians of Canada, and
legal entities owned or controlled by any of them, as a category of
persons in respect of which the Minister of Industry, Science and
Technology may develop and implement programs and projects of special
assistance to aid economic development.
